item.title: Intro
item.author: jacob.braswell00@gmail.com (Jacob Braswell)
item.description: Hello! This is me starting my blog. I am wanting to use this space as a way to share some things that I am learning. Who am I? By way of introduction, I am an MLOps engineer with a background in statistics. I enjoy learning new technologies and concepts and this blog is one way I hope to better learn things myself. I am hoping to post about once a month but we will see if I can keep that cadence in the future.
